headline: Pool (NASDAQ:POOL) Reports Q3 In Line With Expectations
summary: Swimming pool distributor Pool (NASDAQ:POOL) met Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q3 CY2025, with sales up 1.3% year on year to $1.45 billion. Its GAAP profit of $3.40 per share was in line with analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: Pool Corp.: Q3 Earnings Snapshot
summary: POOL on Thursday reported third-quarter profit of $126.5 million. On a per-share basis, the Covington, Louisiana-based company said it had net income of $3.40. Earnings, adjusted for pretax gains, came to $3.39 per share.
